Maintainer: Dave Carlton <davec@mac.com/>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 10)
Standards-Version: 4.1.2
Homepage: https://github.com/tgunr/sanoid

Package: sanoid
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${perl:Depends}, libconfig-inifiles-perl, libcapture-tiny-perl, zfsutils-linux
Recommends: gzip, openssh-client | ssh-clientmbuffer, pv, lzop
Description: Policy-driven snapshot management and replication tools
 A policy-driven snapshot management tool for ZFS filesystems.
 This package includes both sanoid (the snapshot management tool) and
 syncoid (the replication tool) along with syncoid-runner for
 automated replication scheduling.
